   <talk_paragraph index="n833_velskud-1" image="QN_Npc_Lotus_Elder_Teramai.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Velskud$<BR>Go and tell <FONT color=#a82424>Terrence Terramai</FONT>.<BR>Don't interfere in this matter anymore....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-1" image="QN_Npc_Velskud.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-1-a" mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Terrence Terramai$<BR>Hmm, so <FONT color=#a82424>Velskud</FONT> is saying he'll personally take care of Barnac?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-1-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-1-b" mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Terrence Terramai$<BR>Velskud…. Though he may have been thinking of something else at the back of his mind, a part of me still regarded him as an old friend whom I fought alongside with 50 years ago….<BR>I was a fool to expect anything from him….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-1-b" image="QN_Npc_Death_Knight.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-1-c" mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>Terramai....</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Terrence Terramai$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Barnac</FONT> was a hero who saved Alteia....<BR>He has sacrificed himself for this world and the world should at least let him rest in peace.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-1-c" image="QP_Geraint_sword.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-1-d" mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>Did you find another way?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Terrence Terramai$<BR>While you went to meet Cidel, we investigated some things here too. We looked for things other than <FONT color=#a82424>Geraint's sword</FONT> that could suppress the evil curse on Barnac.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-1-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-1-e" mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Terrence Terramai$<BR>That's right. Although it's only a myth that was passed down in Lotus Marsh... We have to try if there is even a small possibility. According to that myth, the good Ancients made an artifact with the Goddess's powers to purify the evil Ancients during the War of the Ancients.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-1-e" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-1-f" mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Terrence Terramai$<BR>That object's name is <FONT color=#a82424>Mirror of Truth</FONT>.<BR>When you look into the Mirror of Truth, the fake self is seen in the mirror and is absorbed by the mirror.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-1-f" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-2" mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>Where can we find the Mirror of Truth?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Terrence Terramai$<BR>If the myth is true, we'd be able to trap those who are controlling Barnac inside the mirror. If we do that, we'll be able to purify Barnac with the Prophet's power.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-2" image="QW_61.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Terrence Terramai$<BR>The temple knights are searching for it in various places. You can go to <FONT color=#a82424>Shadow of Evil Spirits</FONT>. And if you find a mirror that seems holy, immediately retrieve it.<BR>That should be the <FONT color=#a82424>Mirror of Truth</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-3" image="QW_61.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-3-lv_check" mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>There was nothing there.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Terrence Terramai$<BR>Did you find anything at <FONT color=#a82424>Shadow of Evil Spirits</FONT>?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-3-a" image="" itemindex="">
